\">U-shaped kitchen<\/a> in muted colours of white and grey is transformed into a space of style with brass handles. Complementing the industrial vibes exuded by the brick wall, using brass fixtures and a statement chandelier is a coveted choice for any modern home.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/25123610\/modern-kitchen-interior-design.jpg\" alt=\"Modern kitchen interior design in muted colours of white and grey\" class=\"wp-image-49961\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/25123610\/modern-kitchen-interior-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/25123610\/modern-kitchen-interior-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/25123610\/modern-kitchen-interior-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/25123610\/modern-kitchen-interior-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A white marble countertop makes the kitchen opulent <\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern House Interior Design&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Since modern and contemporary are used synonymously, this common area leans more towards modern house interior design. A vibrant, chic space with bold and bright colours is playful and welcoming in equal measure. The use of contrasting prints and shapes is what sets this modern house apart from other traditional choices.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/25123602\/modern-house-interior-design.jpg\" alt=\"Modern house interior design with bold and bright colours for a playful vibe\" class=\"wp-image-49960\" sr