or-design.jpg\" alt=\"Modern classic interior design with warm led lights with hints of grey as focal point\" class=\"wp-image-49959\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/25123555\/modern-classic-interior-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/25123555\/modern-classic-interior-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/25123555\/modern-classic-interior-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/25123555\/modern-classic-interior-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Warm LED lights are a game changer<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Interior Design Styles&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>What modern interior designs mean to you can be the opposite for someone else. But if it is anything that involves ample natural light seeping through over-the-top large windows, this style is your thing. A rustic kitchen-cum-dining space illuminated with fresh air and natural light is a refreshing zone to start your day.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/25123545\/modern-interior-design-style.jpg\" alt=\"Modern interior design style with fresh green plants to add a cheerful vibe\n\" class=\"wp-image-49958\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/25123545\/modern-interior-design-style.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/25123545\/modern-interior-design-style-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/25123545\/modern-interior-design-style-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/25123545\/modern-interior-design-style-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Fresh green plants add a cheerful vibe to the room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Stylish home interior solutions for a modern home\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/16185537\/stylish-home-interior-solutions-for-modern-home.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Duplex House Interior&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When you have the luxury of space, let your creative juices flow freely as you revamp different areas of your home. This stylish informal seating living room can be a more intimate option to host friends and family, while the second living room can have a more formal setting.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/25123536\/modern-duplex-house-interior.jpg\" alt=\"Modern duplex house interior by using bright colours and indian handicrafts\" class=\"wp-image-49957\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/25123536\/modern-duplex-house-interior.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/25123536\/modern-duplex-house-interior-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/25123536\/modern-duplex-house-interior-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/25123536\/modern-duplex-house-interior-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Bright colours &amp; Indian handicrafts dominate this Indo-modern space<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Mid-Century Modern Interior Design&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When you think of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/mid-century-modern-interior-design-ideas\/\">mid-century modern designs<\/a>, you think of outdated styles from a bygone era. But today, it includes a soothing mix of neutral walls, contemporary minimalistic art, and sustainable materials- all of which make up this serene bedroom. Pastel pinks with tones of brown lend a warm, earthy vibe, while the large windows fill the bedroom with calming natural light to make the space a zen-worthy spot.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/25123525\/mid-century-modern-interior-design.jpg\" alt=\"Mid-century modern interior design with an armchair to make a statement\n\" class=\"wp-image-49956\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/25123525\/mid-century-modern-interior-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/25123525\/mid-century-modern-interior-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/25123525\/mid-century-modern-interior-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/25123525\/mid-century-modern-interior-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A statement armchair is an excellent focal point<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Modern Interior Design&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A classic attraction point in any modern room is the use of primary colours. You can use this for accent pieces, artwork, or even as <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/kitchen-backsplash-ideas\/\">kitchen backsplashes<\/a>. The vibrant colours used generously throughout the space add a striking visual appeal to the interior.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/25123517\/modern-interior-design-using-vibrant-colours.jpg\" alt=\"Modern interior design by using vibrant colours to add a striking visual effect\" class=\"wp-image-49955\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/25123517\/modern-interior-design-using-vibrant-colours.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/25123517\/modern-interior-design-using-vibrant-colours-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/25123517\/modern-interior-design-using-vibrant-colours-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/25123517\/modern-interior-design-using-vibrant-colours-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Yellow and grey makes a bold statement<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>These 10 modern interior design ideas are just the beginning of your journey towards curating a home that is more than just a style statement. Want more inspirational ideas? Reach out to us at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">DesignCafe<\/a>, and let us help you turn those ideas into reality.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">FAQs On Modern Interior Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>What role does minimalism play in modern interior design?<\/strong><br>A minimalist approach uses sparing but essential elements to highlight a home. Statement light fixtures, elegant materials, an open layout, and natural materials give the space a sense of freedom.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Can I mix modern design elements with other styles to create a unique look?<\/strong><br>Yes, you can mix modern design elements with other various styles like contemporary or mid-century. For instance, when you have traditional furniture, add contemporary decor elements and light fixtures for a modern flavour.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How do I create a sense of openness and spaciousness in modern interior design?<\/strong><br>Used curved lines to create the illusion of a free-flowing space in the room. Horizontal stripes will make walls seem wider and work well in small homes with little room for furniture. On the other hand, using vertical lines creates the appearance of higher ceilings for a more spacious home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>What materials and textures are used frequently in modern interior design?<\/strong><br>Modern interior design styles use furniture and fixtures with simple forms in materials like wood, leather, glass, and stone. Textures, on the other hand, feature a solid neutral colour palette which can be customised to a homeowner&#8217;s preferences.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Can I use technology and smart features in modern interior design?<\/strong><br>Designers often use technology and smart features in sync with modern aesthetics to create a holistic experience for owners today.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Love modern interior designs? Here are ten tips you need to know.&nbsp; The beauty of modern interior designs lies in its everlasting relevance and versatility to blend with other styles. Today, homeowners are looking to create fuss-free spaces that are comfortable and cosy in equal measure. So, what is modern design? While doing up your&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":36,"featured_media":49965,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":"","_wp_rev_ctl_limit":""},"categories":[12],"tags":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-49954","1":"post","2":"type-post","3":"status-publish","4":"format-standard","5":"has-post-thumbnail","7":"category-home-interiors"},"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v23.6 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>10 Best Tips For Creating A Modern I